---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>AnchorSpec — OpenSpec without the telemetry</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A minimal fork of OpenSpec with telemetry removed and the CLI rebranded. All upstream features preserved." />
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      :root {
        --bg: #0d1117;
        --surface: #161b22;
        --border: #30363d;
        --accent: #58a6ff;
        --text: #e6edf3;
        --muted: #8b949e;
        --green: #3fb950;
      }

      body {
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      header {
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }

      .logo {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .badge {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        color: var(--muted);
        padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
      }

      .header-nav {
        margin-left: auto;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1.25rem;
      }

      .header-nav a {
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .header-nav a:hover { color: var(--text); }

      main {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .tag {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--green);
        border: 1px solid var(--green);
        padding: 0.2rem 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0.85;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.15;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        max-width: 700px;
      }

      h1 span { color: var(--accent); }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        max-width: 520px;
        line-height: 1.65;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        padding: 0.65rem 1.4rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: opacity 0.15s;
      }
      .btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

      .btn-primary {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: #0d1117;
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        background: var(--surface);
        color: var(--text);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .install-block {
        margin-top: 3.5rem;
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        font-family: "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, monospace;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
      }

      .install-block .prompt { color: var(--accent); user-select: none; }
      .install-block code { color: var(--text); }

      .features {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 1px;
        background: var(--border);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-top: 5rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .feature {
        background: var(--surface);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .feature-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
      .feature h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
      .feature p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

      footer {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      footer a { color: var(--muted); }
      footer a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <a class="logo" href="/">⚓️ AnchorSpec</a>
      <nav class="header-nav">
        <a href="/www/docs/v1.3.1/getting-started">Docs</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <span class="tag">❤️ OpenSpec, but need it minus its (minimal) telemetry?</span>

      <h1>OpenSpec features.<br /><span>Zero tracking.</span></h1>

      <p class="subtitle">
        AnchorSpec is a clean fork of OpenSpec with telemetry removed and
        the CLI rebranded to <code>anchorspec</code>. Every upstream feature is
        preserved — just without the phone-home.
      </p>

      <p >

      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://github.com/AnchorSpec/anchorspec">
          View on GitHub
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://github.com/AnchorSpec/anchorspec/releases">
          Releases
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="install-block">
        <span class="prompt">$</span>
        <code>npm install -g anchorspec</code>
      </div>

      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">📴</div>
          <h3>Telemetry stripped</h3>
          <p>All analytics, usage reporting, and outbound tracking removed at the source.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">🟰</div>
          <h3>Full feature parity</h3>
          <p>Every OpenSpec capability is intact — validation, code generation, diffing, and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">🛤️</div>
          <h3>Stays current</h3>
          <p>Tracks upstream OpenSpec releases so you always get the latest features.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">📦</div>
          <h3>Drop-in replacement</h3>
          <p>Same CLI surface as OpenSpec. Swap the binary, keep your existing scripts and workflows.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">🤹</div>
          <h3>Skills included</h3>
          <p><code>ansx</code> is a 1-to-1 replacement for <code>opsx</code></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>⚓️ AnchorSpec is an independent fork, not affiliated with the OpenSpec project. &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="https://github.com/AnchorSpec/AnchorSpec">GitHub</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/anchorspec">NPM</a></p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
